==Translingual==
===Etymology===
formed from the family name ''Malpighiaceae''

===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''''Malpighiales'''''
# {{botany}} a [[botanical name]] at the rank of [[order]]. As with any botanical name, [[circumscription]] and placement of the order depend on [[taxonomic system]] and viewpoint. In practice, there is only a single placement current, in the [[rosids]]. As circumscribed there, it is a very large order. 

